

beV + Perceived   被認為
I don't want to be perceived as lazy.  我不希望被認為是很懶的人。
He is perceived as a very successful person.  他在大眾眼中被認為是一個非常成功的人。
they're perceived by some    他們被某些人認為..


by some 被某些人
by some to be
by some as
It is seen by some as a huge risk. (這被某些人視為巨大的風險。)
He is believed by some to be the best. (他被某些人相信是最棒的。)



